1
00:00:04,817 --> 00:00:06,717
Let's break up.

2
00:00:11,458 --> 00:00:13,229
I'm sorry.

3
00:00:16,157 --> 00:00:17,842
What?

4
00:00:17,842 --> 00:00:21,128
What did you just say? Say that again.

5
00:00:21,128 --> 00:00:23,028
What did you just say?

6
00:00:23,028 --> 00:00:25,467
Nan Hee, the thing is—

7
00:00:25,467 --> 00:00:27,667
You're sorry?

8
00:00:27,667 --> 00:00:29,358
For what?

9
00:00:29,358 --> 00:00:30,778
For toying with me?

10
00:00:30,778 --> 00:00:33,837
Because you have to toss me now that you're done with me?

11
00:00:33,837 --> 00:00:36,178
You want to break up?

12
00:00:36,178 --> 00:00:38,782
Did we make our relationship official?

13
00:00:38,782 --> 00:00:41,066
What is our relationship?

14
00:00:41,066 --> 00:00:42,818
Did you think I would sleep with you whenever you wanted

15
00:00:42,818 --> 00:00:46,218
and let you abandon me when you didn't want me anymore?

16
00:00:52,658 --> 00:00:55,427
You said you were at ease when you were with me.

17
00:00:55,427 --> 00:00:58,940
You said being with me comforted you

18
00:00:58,940 --> 00:01:01,338
and made your heart flutter!

19
00:01:01,338 --> 00:01:05,746
You said that's why you loved me! You said you loved me!

20
00:01:07,408 --> 00:01:09,667
You said you loved me,

21
00:01:10,608 --> 00:01:12,700
but you want to break up with me now

22
00:01:13,318 --> 00:01:15,274
out of the blue

23
00:01:16,017 --> 00:01:17,901
like this?

24
00:01:19,658 --> 00:01:21,777
I'm really sorry.

25
00:01:23,327 --> 00:01:26,427
No. You have no idea.

26
00:01:26,427 --> 00:01:30,348
You have no idea what you should be apologizing for.

27
00:01:30,348 --> 00:01:31,667
There's no sense of respect

28
00:01:31,667 --> 00:01:34,338
in the way you treat me or other people.

29
00:01:34,338 --> 00:01:36,408
You only ramble on and on about being fair, bringing justice,

30
00:01:36,408 --> 00:01:38,337
and having a conscience in front of people,

31
00:01:38,337 --> 00:01:41,877
but you have no clue what it means to respect other people.

32
00:01:42,477 --> 00:01:45,748
So you're worried that your wife might find out about us

33
00:01:45,748 --> 00:01:49,017
because people will find out that you're nothing but a hypocrite!

34
00:01:49,017 --> 00:01:50,917
So you're so afraid that you'll lose what you have,

35
00:01:50,917 --> 00:01:54,417
which you didn't even deserve in the first place!

36
00:01:57,328 --> 00:02:00,968
You're so consumed with the thought of getting rid of me

37
00:02:00,968 --> 00:02:04,963
that you don't even see what you're doing to me.

38
00:02:09,267 --> 00:02:11,778
You were having fun when you were sleeping with me.

39
00:02:11,778 --> 00:02:14,098
I bet it was a thrill.

40
00:02:14,098 --> 00:02:16,878
I'm not asking you to pay for your pleasure.

41
00:02:16,878 --> 00:02:18,617
I'm saying you must at least show respect

42
00:02:18,617 --> 00:02:20,647
to the woman who made you laugh and comforted you.

43
00:02:20,647 --> 00:02:22,532
So,

44
00:02:24,787 --> 00:02:27,607
since you didn't show me any respect,

45
00:02:27,607 --> 00:02:31,059
I will show you the disastrous result

46
00:02:33,598 --> 00:02:36,217
of your action from now on.

47
00:02:39,197 --> 00:02:41,778
I bet you want to kill me.

48
00:02:41,778 --> 00:02:44,167
You want me to die, don't you?

49
00:02:44,167 --> 00:02:46,237
How can you say something like that?

50
00:02:46,237 --> 00:02:48,242
Not yet?

51
00:02:49,208 --> 00:02:53,679
Then I'll make you think just like that.

52
00:02:53,679 --> 00:02:56,682
Nan Hee, where are you going?

53
00:02:56,682 --> 00:02:58,518
Nan Hee!

54
00:02:58,518 --> 00:03:02,086
Nan Hee! It's dangerous!

55
00:03:02,086 --> 00:03:06,200
When have you ever worried about me?

56
00:03:07,092 --> 00:03:11,342
I'm going to die!

57
00:03:12,867 --> 00:03:14,652
If I die,

58
00:03:14,652 --> 00:03:18,100
you will feel a sense of guilt, even if it's small.

59
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:20,688
I will break your heart!

60
00:03:20,688 --> 00:03:22,078
Nan Hee.

61
00:03:22,078 --> 00:03:23,678
Then...

62
00:03:25,477 --> 00:03:29,301
you will realize what you have done to me.

63
00:03:30,448 --> 00:03:32,818
- I'm sorry. It's my fault. 
 - Let go of me!

64
00:03:32,818 --> 00:03:35,985
- I'm sorry. It's my fault. 
 - Let go!

65
