67
00:04:14,428 --> 00:04:16,027
What happened?

68
00:04:16,027 --> 00:04:19,920
I texted you, but you never texted back. I got worried.

69
00:04:21,737 --> 00:04:24,542
Sorry, I didn't check your text.

70
00:04:27,948 --> 00:04:29,948
I'll go wash up.

71
00:04:29,948 --> 00:04:31,648
Nan Hee,

72
00:04:35,548 --> 00:04:37,632
did you cry?

73
00:04:37,632 --> 00:04:39,977
You met Na Geun Woo, right?

74
00:04:40,858 --> 00:04:42,914
Did something happen?

75
00:04:44,027 --> 00:04:45,947
He wanted to break up.

76
00:04:50,198 --> 00:04:52,218
That's for the better.

77
00:04:52,897 --> 00:04:56,068
You shouldn't even cry about that. This was supposed to happen.

78
00:04:56,068 --> 00:04:58,275
I told him no.

79
00:04:58,275 --> 00:04:59,786
What?

80
00:05:00,737 --> 00:05:02,207
I can't break up with him.

81
00:05:02,207 --> 00:05:04,948
- Nan Hee. 
 - I can't.

82
00:05:04,948 --> 00:05:08,528
I can't break up with him yet. I still have so much to do.

83
00:05:09,688 --> 00:05:11,932
You should end it here.

84
00:05:11,932 --> 00:05:15,227
What if you get hurt from this? This would've been all for nothing.

85
00:05:15,227 --> 00:05:17,427
You should stop here. I'm sure you can find other ways.

86
00:05:17,427 --> 00:05:19,164
No.

87
00:05:19,164 --> 00:05:20,964
There is none.

88
00:05:20,964 --> 00:05:24,198
I tried out everything else I could, but nothing worked.

89
00:05:24,198 --> 00:05:26,437
I finally started to get on their nerves.

90
00:05:26,437 --> 00:05:29,437
How can I stop now? I can't give up now.

91
00:05:31,008 --> 00:05:33,668
I would've never started in the first place,

92
00:05:33,668 --> 00:05:36,097
if I was afraid of getting hurt.

93
00:05:37,818 --> 00:05:43,138
I should bet my life to give them a taste of their own medicine.

94
00:05:45,058 --> 00:05:47,493
Nan Hee.

95
00:05:47,493 --> 00:05:49,486
Let me go and wash up.

96
